"uid":47052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T12:15:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dced220f615b0f862b8b3cbd172ae75e108b5f90","tid":1842887,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T12:38:03.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我準備好同醫護一齊罷工<br />\n<br />\n借位<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[行動post] 武漢肺炎係上天賜比香港人打爆港共嘅機會，做嘢啦！！！</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1838198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1838198</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我要真雙普選！</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DVXbXsc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDVXbXsc.jpg&h=ab82b961&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d8fa097a41416defa35563ffe8acf856babe1ab","tid":1842887,"uid":137204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T13:48:52.000Z","msg":"講得啱 唔係中共研發呢個病毒冇可能毒到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}